text: Norman Morris (9 May 1907 - 15 July 1982) was an Australian cricketer. He played four first-class matches for New South Wales in 1928/29. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1907 births Category:1982 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
